description.@value: An iconography research paper related to the Kizil Caves.  Comprised of the main text and a total of 25 original colors prints.  The German expedition did not number of the grottoes, but named them according to their characteristics. This text describes the peacock cave, navigators cave, canyon cave, feet-washing cave, treasure cave and Maya cave.
